<F P=106> [Article by Yu. A. Izrael, Ye. M. Artemov, I. M. Nazarov, </F>
Sh. D. Fridman, V. I. Zinenko, A. I. Krivoshapko, N. G. 
Lyashchenko, V. G. Pakhomov, V. A. Chirkov and Ye. D. Stukin, 
Global Climate and Ecology Institute, Russian Committee for 
