<H3> <TI>   Yablokov Faults Government Bureaucracy for Lack of Ecological Progress </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94WN0124A Moscow MOSKOVSKIYE NOVOSTI in Russian No 48, 28 
Nov 93 p B7 </F>

